The Alex Jones Show
Sunday, 20 February 2011


[sebaygo1]


The 2 hour Sunday show is typically a review of the past week's news and a look forward to the coming week's events.

The Infowars web site describes today's broadcast as follows.

On this important Sunday edition of The Alex Jones Show, Alex discusses the developing situation in Libya, Iranian naval ships crossing the Suez canal, thumb scanning to buy and sell goods, the ongoing struggle for freedom in Egypt, and more.
